This fork modifies Blockbench for Vintage Story-focused cuboid model editing.
Modified-work notice: Vintage Bench changes began on 2026-06-22 and continue
through later release commits. See CHANGELOG.md and source history for dated
modification details.

The first cleanup pass removes or disables user-facing Minecraft-specific
formats, Bedrock-specific workflows, mesh-modeling features, and hosted web
application behavior while preserving the desktop cuboid editing base.

